## 💡 Key Concepts
- `AzureWebApp@1` deploys a zip package to App Service
- `startUpCommand` overrides the default startup for Linux apps
- Health check after deploy validates the deployment succeeded
- `condition: succeeded()` prevents deploy if build failed
